('New Tutorial: How to Manage Static Content', '<p>Learn how to add, edit and manage static content.</p>', '<p>Watch this tutorial and learn how to add, edit and manage static content from the admin panel. It&#39;s simple and easy!</p><p><em>WorksForWeb Software Tutorial - Managing Static Content</em></p><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3U-X_euoXPk\" width=\"420\"></iframe></p>', 1, '2016-05-31 06:00:00', ''),
('Update of Video Tutorial Library: Setting Up Image Carousel', '<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The new video tutorial &quot;</span>Image Carousel<span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&quot; is available.</span></p>', '<p>Want to learn a specific tool of our classifieds scripts in depth?&nbsp;This is a great introduction to &quot;Image Carousel&quot; that will take you through all its settings.</p><p><em>WorksForWeb Software Tutorial - Image Carousel</em></p><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_P_SoVKdWY4\" width=\"420\"></iframe></p>', 1, '2016-05-10 06:00:00', ''),
('Steps to Configure Currency Converter Addon in the New Video Tutorial', '<p>Explore some tips for using Currency Converter Addon&nbsp;with our new video tutorial.</p>', '<p>Explore some tips for using Currency Converter Addon&nbsp;with our new video tutorial. Configure Currency Converter Addon properly and make your website more productive.</p><p><em>WorksForWeb Video Tutorial - Currency Converter Addon</em></p><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xS-PuBA66BY\" width=\"420\"></iframe></p>', 1, '2016-02-16 06:00:00', ''),
('Video Guide in Managing Sub-Administrator Addon', '<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">The new video tutorial &quot;</span>Sub-Administrator Addon<span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">&quot; is available.</span></p>', '<p>Do you want to learn &quot;Sub-Administrator Addon&quot;? Don&#39;t waste your time, watch our video tutorial that will teach you how to manage this addon, how to adjust the functions your particular administrator will be able to access.</p><p><em>WorksForWeb Software Tutorial - Sub-Administrator Addon</em></p><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mNYdsrTlXOI\" width=\"420\"></iframe></p>', 1, '2016-01-13 06:00:00', ''),
('Christmas Contest Results', '<p><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Would you like to know what happened with the award of our Christmas contest?</span></p>', '<p>Would you like to know what happened with the award of our Christmas contest? We took our time with it, and we finally made a decision. &nbsp;For more information: &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/publications/pimpin-your-website-contest-results/\">Pimpin&rsquo; Your Website Contest Results</a>&nbsp;.</p>', 1, '2016-01-11 06:00:00', ''),
('Country Package for Sri Lanka Available', '<p>There is a localization package for Sri Lanka available for our new and existing customers.</p>', '<p> There is a localization package for Sri Lanka available for our new and existing customers. Please contact our <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/company/contact-us/pre-sales-inquiry/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sales Dept</a> for details on what this country package includes.</p><p>Worksforweb offers a number of localization packages called <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/services/custom-solutions/country-packages/\" title=\"All Country Packages for Scripts by WorksForWeb\">Country Packs for a number of countries</a>, and the list is constantly growing. If you need a country package for your country, which is not on our list yet, please get in touch with Sales, and we&#39;ll be happy to create one for you.</p>', 1, '2016-01-05 06:00:00', ''),
('Announcing the Release of the New Version 7.4.0', '<p>We are pleased to announce the launch of the new version 7.4.0.</p>', '<p>Today we are delighted to announce the launch of the new version 7.4.0 of iAuto, iRealty, iLister, iAuto Bikes, iLister Heavy Machinery, iLister Pets, iLister Guns for Sale, iLister Caravans, and iLister Models.</p><p>New additions in version 7.4.0:</p><ul class=\"bullet\"><li>Adding Comments to User Accounts;</li><li>Recent Listings by Different Categories in Different Blocks;</li><li>All Featured or Sponsored Ads in One Click;</li><li>Advanced Search Improved;</li><li>Under Construction Mode;</li><li>YouTube ID in Feed Import Mapping;</li><li>Added Geo Code Search;</li><li>Pages Can Be Closed from Indexing;</li><li>Emails from Admin to Users;</li><li>Bye-bye, iAuto Bikes Green Theme;</li><li>Adding Listings Based On Other Listing Data;</li><li>Other Minor Design and Code Improvements and Bugfixes.</li></ul><p>Please visit the <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/publications/under-construction-mode-and-pages-prevented-from-indexing-in-v74/\">official release page</a> to read more about all the changes and improvements introduced in the current version.</p><p></p><p>We have already upgraded all our online demo websites to the latest versions, check them out by following the links below:</p><ul class=\"bullet\"><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iRealty/demo/\" title=\"iRealty Real Estate Script\">iRealty Real Estate Script</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iAuto/demo/\" title=\"iAuto Automobile Classified Script\">iAuto Auto Classified Script</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iLister/demo/\" title=\"iLister General Purpose Classified Script\">iLister General Classified Script</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iAuto-Bikes/demo/\" title=\"iAutoBikes Motorcycle Classifieds Software\">iAutoBikes Motorcycle Classifieds Software</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iLister-Pets/demo/\" title=\"iListerPets Pet Classifieds Script\">iListerPets Pet Classifieds Script</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iLister-Machinery/demo/\" title=\"iLister Heavy Machinery Classifieds Script\">iLister Heavy Machinery Script</a></li></ul><p><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/support/free-trial/\" rel=\"nofollow\">You can download fully-functional copies</a> of our products for installation on your server. Once installed, you can modify anything and everything. You are not going to lose any of the changes once you purchase a permanent license.</p><p>Our <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/company/contact-us/pre-sales-inquiry/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sales Team</a> is always ready to provide you with more details and answers to your questions regarding our classified products.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>', 1, '2015-12-16 06:00:00', ''),
('Pimpin’ Your Website! Pimpin’ It FREE!', '<p>Do you have a website that needs a total makeover but you can&rsquo;t afford it? We&rsquo;re starting a contest &ldquo;Pimpin&rsquo; Your Website! Pimpin&rsquo; It FREE!&rdquo;</p>', '<p>Do you have a website that needs a total makeover but you can&rsquo;t afford it? We&rsquo;re starting a contest &ldquo;Pimpin&rsquo; Your Website! Pimpin&rsquo; It FREE!&rdquo; We will award a mega Christmas gift to ONE of our customers whose website needs a boost!</p><p>Contest is now officially ON! Ends on Christmas Day, 25 Dec, 2015.</p><p>Check out our <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/publications/pimp-your-website-free/\">Contest page</a> as Christmas is almost here. Post a few words about your dream on <a href=\"http://facebook.com/worksforweb.classifieds\">our FB Wall</a>.</p>', 1, '2015-12-15 06:00:00', ''),
