('Version 7.3.0 Is Launched!', '<p>The best end-of-summer event for our customers is the launch of the new version 7.3.0 of iAuto, iRealty, iLister, iAuto Bikes, iLister Heavy Machinery, iLister Pets, iLister Guns for Sale, iLister Caravans, and iLister Models.</p>', '<p>The best end-of-summer event for our customers is the launch of the new version 7.3.0 of iAuto, iRealty, iLister, iAuto Bikes, iLister Heavy Machinery, iLister Pets, iLister Guns for Sale, iLister Caravans, and iLister Models.</p><p></p><p>New additions in version 7.3.0:</p><ul class=\"bullet\"><li>New responsive Bootstrap Blue Theme for all products;</li><li>Improvements in a new theme creation;</li><li>Bye-bye, iRealty Green Theme;</li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/addons/facebook-comments-addon/\">Facebook Comments, a new module</a>;</li><li>Implementation of block cache;</li><li>Improved listing image displaying;</li><li>Fixed third-party login via Facebook;</li><li>Ads On Map - paging integration;</li><li>Fixed WebMoney Payment Gateway;</li><li>Mechanisms of video displaying was changed. From this version video has to be uploaded via YouTube and YouTube Data API.</li><li>Facebook Share Button is integrated instead of Facebook repost.</li><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/server-requirements/\">Minimum server requirements</a> was changed.</li><li>Other minor improvements and bugfixes.</li></ul><p>Please visit the <a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/publications/new-template-theme-and-facebook-comments-module-in-v73/\">official release page</a> to read more about all the changes and improvements introduced in the current version.</p><p>We have already upgraded all our online demo websites to the latest versions, check them out by following the links below:</p><ul class=\"bullet\"><li><a href=\"http://www.worksforweb.com/classifieds-software/iRealty/demo/\" title=\"iRealty Real Estate Script\">iRealty Real Estate Script</a></li><li><a hr