('WorksForWeb Software Tutorial - How To Adjust Basic Theme Colors Quickly', '<p>The new video tutorial &quot;How To Adjust Basic Theme Colors Quickly&quot; is available.</p>', '<p>The new video tutorial &quot;How To Adjust Basic Theme Colors Quickly&quot; is available. This video tutorial shows you how to easily modify the look of your website with only a few simple clicks.</p><p><em>WorksForWeb Software Tutorial - How To Adjust Basic Theme Colors Quickly</em></p><p><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"236\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9g5wcfN7w78\" width=\"420\"></iframe></p>', 1, '2015-08-12 06:00:00', 'http://www.worksforweb.com/getImage.php?id=1326'),
('Model Agency Classified Script Released', '<p>An awesome product was released &ndash; Model Agency Classified Script. This product is actually unique as it takes little effort and time to set up a ready-made business.</p>', '<p>We are excited to present a new product in our continuously growing line of classified scripts. This time it is a Model Agency Directory Script. It is unique in a way of presenting model portfolio and is one of a kind business solution ready-made for the fashion and modelling industries.</p><p>Try the new product on the online demo:<br /><a href=\"http://demo.worksforweb.com/Model-Agency/\" target=\"_blank\">Live Model Agency Classified Script Demo</a></p><p>You are welcome to contact, email or chat with our Sales Team. Please send your requests to <a href=\"/company/contact-us/pre-sales-inquiry/\" target=\"_blank\">our Sales Team</a>. We&#39;ll be happy to address your inquiries.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 1, '2014-12-03 06:00:00', 'http://www.worksforweb.com/getImage.php?id=1303');
